TempMail
========
Tempmail is temporary mail forwarder which hosted on [tempmail.ir](http://tempmail.ir)

How to install it?
----------
Tempmail contains two important forlder,web and mailer.
Web is interface of it to create email and ...
Mailer is heart of tempmail which forward emails.

Just copy them on your host,create database and set username,password and db name in web/index.php mailer/pipe.php

Then pipe all email to pipe.php.


